\c 3
\s Yambiro yaPauro pamusoro pekururama kwevanhu
\p
\v 1 Pakupedzisira, hama dzangu, farai muna Ishe. Kukunyoreraizve zvinhu zvimwechetezvo, kwandiri zvirokwazvo hazvinetesi, asi kwamuri zviri pachena.
\v 2 Chenjererai imbwa, chenjererai vabati vakaipa, chenjererai vekucheka;
\v 3 nekuti isu tiri kudzingiswa, vanoshumira Mwari muMweya, tichizvirumbidza muna Kristu Jesu, uye tisina chivimbo munyama;
\v 4 kunyange ini ndingavawo nechivimbo munyama; kana kune umwe unofunga kuvimba nenyama, zvikuru ini;
\v 5 ndakadzingiswa nezuva rerusere, \add ndiri\add* werudzi rwaIsraeri, \add we\add*dzinza raBenjamini, muHebheru wevaHebheru; zviri zvemurairo \add ndiri\add* muFarisi,
\v 6 maererano nekushingaira, ndichishusha kereke; zviri zvekururama kuri mumurairo ndisina chandingapomerwa.
\v 7 Asi zvinhu zvaiva fuma kwandiri, ndizvo zvandakaverenga sekurashikirwa nekuda kwaKristu.
\v 8 Hongu zvirokwazvo, uye ndinoverenga zvinhu zvose \add se\add*kurashikirwa nekuda kwekunakisisa kweruzivo rwaKristu Jesu Ishe wangu, wandakarashikirwa nezvinhu zvose nekuda kwake, ndikazviidza marara, kuti ndiwane Kristu;
\v 9 uye ndiwanikwe maari, ndisina kururama kwangu kunobva kumurairo, asi uko kwerutendo rwaKristu, kururama kunobva kuna Mwari nerutendo;
\v 10 kuti ndimuzive iye, nesimba rekumuka kwake, nekudyidzana kwematambudziko ake, nditodze kufa kwake,
\v 11 kana zvingagoneka ndisvike pakumuka kwevakafa.
\v 12 Handi\add revi\add* kuti ndakato\add chi\add*wana, kana ndakatokwaniswa, asi ndinotevera, kuti zvimwe ndichibate, icho Kristu Jesu chaakambondibatira.
\v 13 Hama, ini handizviverengi kuti ndachibata, asi \add ndinoita\add* chinhu chimwe, ndichikanganwa zvinhu zviri shure, ndichinanavira zvinhu zviri mberi,
\v 14 ndinoteverera kuchinangwa, kumubairo wekudana kwekumusoro kwaMwari muna Kristu Jesu.
\v 15 Naizvozvo isu tose takakwana, ngative nemufungo wakadaro; uye kana zvimwe imwi mune umwe mufungo, Mwari uchakuratidzai kunyange izvi.
\v 16 Asi pane patasvika, ngatifambe nemurairo iwoyu tifunge chinhu ichochi.
\v 17 Hama, ivai vatevedzeri vangu pamwe, natsai kutarira avo vanofamba saizvozvo sezvatakava muenzaniso.
\v 18 Nekuti vazhinji vanofamba, vandakakuvudzai nezvavo kazhinji, nazvino ndinokuvudzai kunyange nekuchema, vavengi vemuchinjikwa waKristu;
\v 19 kuguma kwavo kuparadzwa, mwari wavo \add i\add*dumbu \add ravo\add*, uye kurumbidzwa \add kwavo\add* \add kuri\add* mukunyadzwa, vanofunga zvenyika.
\v 20 Nekuti ubwo hwedu hwuri kumatenga, uko kwatakataririrakowo kuuya kwemuponesi Ishe Jesu Kristu;
\v 21 uyo uchavandudza muviri wekuninipiswa kwedu, kuti ufananidzwe nemuviri wekubwinya kwake, nesimba iro raanogonawo naro kuisa zvinhu zvose pasi pake.
